                    </div>
                    <div style="padding-top:20px;text-align:justify">
                        The said flat is Built on Sy. No.{!Booking__c.Project1__r.Survey_Number__c} situated at {!Booking__c.Project1__r.Project_Address__c} in the Project known as <strong>‘{!Booking__c.Project1__r.Name}’</strong>.
                    </div>
