                         We further declare that we have received the entire sale consideration amount in full and final settlement and there are no pending dues.
                    </div >
                    <div style="padding-top:20px;text-align:justify">
                        It is now confirmed that <span style="background:yellow"><strong>{!Booking__c.salutation_Applicant1__c} {!Booking__c.First_Applicant_Name__c}</strong></span>, have become the absolute owner of the said flat.
                    </div>
                    <div style="padding-top:20px;">
                        We wish you a healthy and prosperous living.
                    </div>
                    <div style="padding-top:20px;">
                        <strong>for Mahendra Homes Private Limited</strong>
                    </div>
                   <div style="padding-top:80px;">
                       <strong>Authorised Signatory</strong>
                    </div>
                </apex:outputPanel>
            </div>
        </body>
    </html>
</apex:page>